org.insurancedb.data
Class InsuranceCompanyTextDAO

java.lang.Object
  org.insurancedb.data.InsuranceCompanyTextDAO

public class InsuranceCompanyTextDAO
extends java.lang.Object

InsuranceCompanyTextDAO is an implementation of the data access object. It uses a text file database to manage records and implements the Singleton pattern.
